    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>High-intensity discharge lamps in which the major portion of the light is produced by radiation of metal halides and their products of dissociation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000021051/Kaufman and Christensen, IES Lighting Handbook (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ontladingslampen van een grote intensiteit waarin het grootste deel van het licht wordt geproduceerd door middel van straling van metalen halides en de producten die zij afscheiden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>高強度放電燈的一種，主要是藉由金屬鹵化物及其解離原子的輻射而產生光。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hochdruck-Entladungslampe, in der der große Teil des Lichts durch Strahlung von Metallhalogeniden und deren Dissoziationsprodukten erzeugt wird.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
